item.description: This is a great place with plenty of rolling hills.. I will lead the group on an off-leash brisk paced hike. The forest lies along Mayflower St. about a half mile beyond the transfer station. Mayflower is off of Route 3A. Please plan for 2 hours in the woods. If you get misplaced on your way there, you can call my cell. (508) 559-3677

group.name: The South Shore Dog Lovers Pack Walk
